{
  "stem": "8.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we arrived there, it was the day before Christmas, and the wind and the snow would blow in and would cover us, practically.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We-- we did get some thin blankets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we used to fight over the blankets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And me and my mother fought over who should cover.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My mother wanted me to have both blankets, and I wanted here to have the blanket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one day she got so mad at me that she slapped me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so then we decided we will cover with two blankets both of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So that was the solution.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was never hit before in my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had to get up about 4 o'clock in the morning and march to about 10 kilometers to the place of work, which was in Reichenbach-- no, which was in Langenbielau.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had to march on the road, and we passed by civilian areas.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I don't remember, you know, being that close to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember seeing houses in the background.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The road usually was full of snow and ice, and it was terribly hard to walk on them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the-- the platform, the wooden platform, would not bend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the snow would create a ball under our-- and we could not keep our balance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We often would fall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And if we fell, that was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We would be shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We would not-- it was not allowed to fall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So that we would carry the weakest person always in the middle and so that we could help and carry that person.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I remember my cousin-- we took my cousin once into the middle because she just did not want to walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She wanted to just give up.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
